quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  17,67,"“Ndipo akakupezani masautso pa nyanja, amasowa amene mumakhala mukuwapembedza kupatula Iye (Allah). Koma akakupulumutsirani kumtunda, mukutembenuka ndi kunyoza Allah. Ndithu munthu ndi wokana (mtendere wa Allah sayamika)"
  17,68,"“Kodi mukudziika pa chitetezo ndi chilango cha Allah (mukafika pa ntunda) kuti Allah sangakulowetseni pansi mbali iliyonse ya pa ntunda, kapena sangakutumizireni chigumula chamchenga (kapena miyala) kenako inu simudzapeza mtetezi (wokupulumutsani ku chilangocho)"
  17,69,"“Kapena mwadziika pachitetezo kuti (Allah) sadzakubwezeraninso m’nyanjamo kachiwiri ndipo nkudzakutumizirani chimphepo chaukali ndikukumizani chifukwa cha kusakhulupirira (ndi kusathokoza kwanu,) kenako inu nkusapeza wokutetezani kwa Ife"
  17,70,“Ndipo ndithu tawalemekeza ana a Adam; ndipo tawapatsa zokwera pa ntunda ndi pa nyanja; tawapatsa zopatsa zabwino kwambiri; ndipo tawapatsa ulemelero kuposa zambiri m’zomwe tidalenga; ulemelero waukulu kwabasi
  17,71,"“(Akumbutse za) tsiku lomwe tidzaitana anthu onse m’dzina la mneneri wawo; choncho, amene adzapatsidwe akaundula awo ndi dzanja lamanja iwo adzawerenga akaundula awowo (mwachisangalalo), ndipo sadzaponderezedwa ngakhale pa (kachinthu kakang’ono monga) kaulusi ka mkati mwa njere ya kanjeza"
  17,72,"“Ndipo amene ali wakhungu pano (pa dziko lapansi posapenya zizindikiro) adzakhalanso wakhungu pa tsiku la chimaliziro, ndipo adzakhala wosokera kwambiri njira (kumeneko)"
  17,73,"“Ndipo ndithu adatsala pang’ono kukusokoneza pa zimene tavumbulutsa kwa iwe kuti utipekere zina zake m’malo mwa izi; pamenepo, akadakusankha kukhala bwenzi (lawo)"
  17,74,"“Ndipo tikadapanda kukulimbikitsa, ukadapendekera kwa iwo, kupendekera kwa pang’ono"
  17,75,“Tero ndithu tikadakulawitsa chilango chachikulu cha moyo (wa pa dziko lapansi) ndi chilango chachikulu utafa; kenako siukadapeza mthandizi wokupulumutsa kwa Ife